messages.message:
Everyone - We have added a native Spreadsheet viewer in AI Hub release-24.12.0 for internal users.

This enables viewing excel files natively (instead of the current pdf view). You can enable by toggling the `Enable spreadsheet viewer` feature flag in settings. Here is a doc with details of the feature and limitations (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ocA9fP0HN01mQvcR5RPEG0I0fGnzQ8kOyRAQZQxZKjw/edit#heading=h.ni6v5aj848tq).

Please feel free to test and give feedback on the UX, or if you find any issues.

@Lee @joshbronko @Matt Weaver @JD @Aayush @Rakesh
